data.description: Location! Location! Welcome to 75 Bay Ridge Parkway, this semi-detached single family home in the heart of Bay Ridge will have you making everlasting memories. Upon entering through the generous enclosed porch, you will find tons of original charm. This classic home boasts hardwood floors, crown moldings, fireplace, formal dining room and renovated eat-in kitchen with sliding glass doors to the back deck, perfect for your morning coffee. Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a walk-up attic with plenty of space for your imagination to thrive. Full basement with bathroom, laundry, and a side entrance leading to shared driveway with a 1 car garage and backyard. This home is perfectly nestled between the beautiful parks of Shore Road Promenade and the ever so lively 3rd & 5th Avenue dining, salons, and shopping. Close to express buses x27 & x37 and local buses, R train, NYC Ferry, and NYU Langone Hospital. The house dimensions are 17 x 46 situated on a 23 x 94 lot. Total sq. ft. does not include attic and basement. Book your private showing today and make this house your new home with memories to fill decades to come.
